ğŸ“¦ Installation

Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/<your-username>/finova-financial-engine.git
cd finova-financial-engine


Create virtual environment:

python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate


Install dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt

â–¶ï¸ Running the API Locally
uvicorn main:app --reload


Then visit:

ğŸ‘‰ http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs (Swagger UI)

ğŸ§ª Running Tests
